    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-06-03T09:29:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-06-03T09:29:00-05:00" n="243"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d243">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 861.00/1965</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Russia</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_FDR1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Francis</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Vologda</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-06-03T19:00:00+04:31">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 3, 1918, 7 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received June 7, 6.42 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>241. Am just leaving for Petrograd. Have arranged for forwarding cables. In my
                    judgment Czecho-Slovaks should not be disarmed, consequently am instructing
                    Consulate General to inform Soviet government that the Allies would consider
                    disarmament and severe treatment as inspired by Germany or certainly by hostile
                    sentiment toward the Allies.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_FDR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Francis</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
